data.name: textBox12.Value
data.value: = Format("{0:N0}",Fields.dosage) + " " + IIf(Fields.unitDesc = "Suspension" Or Fields.unitDesc = "Syrup" Or Fields.unitDesc = "Drops", "ML", IIf(Fields.unitDesc = "Tablet" Or Fields.unitDesc = "Softgel", "Tablet/s", IIf(Fields.unitDesc = "Capsule", "Capsule/s", IIf(Fields.unitDesc = "Nebule", Fields.unitDesc, IIf(Fields.unitDesc = "Cream", "Apply", IIf(Fields.unitDesc = "Respule", Fields.unitDesc, IIf(Fields.unitDesc = "Sachet", Fields.unitDesc, ""))))))) + " x " + Fields.perDay + " a Day"

data.name: sqlDataSource1.SelectCommand
data.value: select MedicalPrescription.rxID, MedicalPrescription.personnelID, OutgoingItems.productCode, OutgoingItems.qtyRx, OutgoingItems.dosage, OutgoingItems.perDay, OutgoingItems.noDay, ProductList.productDesc, Personnel.personnel_lastName, Personnel.personnel_firstName, Personnel.personnel_midInit, Personnel.personnel_extName, ProductUnit.unitDesc, Personnel.title, Personnel.licenseNo from MedicalPrescription LEFT JOIN OutgoingItems on MedicalPrescription.rxID = OutgoingItems.rxID LEFT JOIN ProductList on ProductList.productCode = OutgoingItems.productCode LEFT JOIN Personnel on Personnel.personnelID = MedicalPrescription.personnelID LEFT JOIN ProductUnit on ProductUnit.unitID = ProductList.unitID where MedicalPrescription.rxID = @rxID
